    <p><span>A member of the Holy Order of the Almighty who once fought the Demon King.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,413 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a> has released the sixth character trailer for <em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest VII Reimagined [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined">Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</a></em>, introducing Sir Mervyn, a member of the Holy Order of the Almighty who once fought the Demon King. <span id="more-1013676"></span></p><p>Sir Mervyn’s character description reads, “A member of the Holy Order of the Almighty, he once fought the Demon King alongside the very deity he worships. Skilled in a variety of sword techniques, he still possesses the skills that earned him the title of hero.”</p><p><em>Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,032 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,438 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [778 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,103 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,060 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2499860/DRAGON_QUEST_VII_Reimagined/" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined/9nkm0ckchdqx" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on February 5, 2026 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-announced-for-ps5-xbox-series-switch-2-switch-and-pc">here</a> <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/09/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-details-visuals-story-features-characters-and-battle-system">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/11/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined-details-adult-kiefer-storyline-stone-tablet-fragments">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Sir Mervyn</span></h2><p><iframe title="『ドラゴンクエストVII Reimagined』キャラクター紹介　メルビン編⛵" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/X6LF0GXjlb8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
